#: ../../doc/manual/manual.en.xml:1958
msgid ""
"</inlinemediaobject> green if you control the unit and it hasn't moved this "
"turn,"
msgstr ""
"</inlinemediaobject> verde si controlas la unidad y no se ha movido este "
